1. Nemoj da me *prevariš*. (Don't cheat me.)
2. On je počinio *prevaru*. (He committed fraud.)
3. To je najveća *prevara* u istoriji. (That's the biggest scam in history.)
4. Ne mogu verovati da je bio uključen u ovu *prevaru*. (I can't believe he was involved in this deception.)
5. Ona je bila žrtva *prevaranata*. (She was a victim of swindlers.)
6. Njihov proizvod je lažna *prevara*. (Their product is a fake scam.)
7. Sudija je smatrao da je to bila namerna *prevara*. (The judge believed it was deliberate fraud.)
8. Imao sam lošu sreću da budem žrtva *prevaranta*. (I was unlucky to be a victim of a fraudster.)
9. Njen bivši dečko ju je *prevario* sa njenom najboljom drugaricom. (Her ex-boyfriend cheated on her with her best friend.)
10. Razotkrivanje *prevara* u kompaniji dovelo je do njenog bankrota. (Uncovering frauds in the company led to its bankruptcy.)